data.description: Welcome to Aspen Village Condominiums!  This quiet gated community, located in a prime area of West Covina features this spacious and well maintained 2 bedroom and 2 bath condo.  Upon stepping into the wide entryway you'll immediately notice the vaulted ceilings which showcase a unique brick fireplace.  This home features TWO enclosed patios.  The master bedroom, has its own private bathroom and walk-in closet.  Step out onto the main patio from the Master bedroom and enjoy a cool drink on the patio!
